title: Agaricales Part 6: Family Amanitaceae (The Hallucinogenic Amanitas)

media:group.media:title: Agaricales Part 6: Family Amanitaceae (The Hallucinogenic Amanitas)
media:group.media:description:
Here we wrap up with Agaricales, and we finish the ones that I know everyone was waiting for, the hallucinogenic Amanitas! Yes, these are the ones Mario eats to get bigger. They also have a hand in the origin of the Santa Claus myth, believe it or not! Want to know more? Press play!

Script by William Marcus

Some of the mushroom photography was provided by Stephen Axford of Planet Fungi. For more dazzling footage check out Stephen's fungi safari in the forests of the Himalayas documenting over 200 species of mushrooms! I'm serious, it's incredible, go watch the trailer: https://www.planetfungi.movie/
